dcterms:description: The dataset is composed of observations on 37215 households collected annually by the Central Statistical Office of Poland (GUS). It includes various variables such as equivalent monthly income, age of the household head, education level, number of persons, and subjective evaluations related to material position and needs satisfaction.
dcterms:title: Polish household budget survey data

dcterms:description: Data collected by the Central Statistical Office of Poland (GUS) that includes various socio-economic variables used for analyzing household budgets and income distributions.
dcterms:title: Central Statistical Office of Poland (GUS) data
